Here I will layout the steps to run a simulation of the Husky

Installing simulation packages
---------------------------------
Follow instructions from link here: https://clearpathrobotics.com/assets/guides/foxy/husky/HuskyInstallSoftware.html

Only do the installing from debian packages and not installing from source

Once installation is finished verify it is working by running the following command
ros2 launch husky_gazebo husky_playpen.launch.py

You can follow this page to verify installation for husky simulation packages: 
https://clearpathrobotics.com/assets/guides/foxy/husky/HuskySimulation.html


